At this stage, I think you'll be the first user of this API so I'm happy to modify OperationIdgenerator with something like below instead:
abstract class OperationIdGenerator {
  abstract fun apply(operationDocument: String, name: String, packageName: String)

  // overridee for batch handling
  open fun generateOperationOutput(operationList: OperationList): OperationOutput {
    operationList.map {
      apply(it.source, it.name, it.packageName) to it
    }
  }

  // change version here everytime the implementation of this class changes
  val version: String
}

Or if we want an interface:
interface BatchOperationIdGenerator {
  fun generateOperationOutput(operationList: OperationList): OperationOutput

  // change version here everytime the implementation of this class changes
  val version: String
}
